### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### Track — page_view
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "user-123",
  "event_type": "page_view",
  "properties": {
    "page": "/home",
    "referrer": "google.com"
  },
  "context": {
    "device": "mobile",
    "session_id": "sess-abc"
  }
}

###

### Track — purchase
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "user-123",
  "event_type": "purchase",
  "properties": {
    "product_id": "prod-456",
    "price": 89.99,
    "currency": "EUR"
  }
}

###

### Track — click
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "user-456",
  "event_type": "click",
  "properties": {
    "element": "buy-now-button",
    "page": "/products/winter-jacket"
  }
}

###

### Track — add_to_cart
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "user-456",
  "event_type": "add_to_cart",
  "properties": {
    "product_id": "prod-789",
    "quantity": 2
  }
}

###

### Track — search
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "user-789",
  "event_type": "search",
  "properties": {
    "query": "winter jacket",
    "results_count": 42
  }
}

###

### Track — custom
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "user-789",
  "event_type": "custom",
  "properties": {
    "action": "newsletter_signup",
    "source": "footer"
  }
}

###

### Track — with explicit event_id (deduplication test)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "evt_dedup-test-001",
  "customer_id": "user-123",
  "event_type": "page_view",
  "properties": {
    "page": "/checkout"
  }
}

